Add Vagrantfile

This allows creating a nice Linux environment with Docker installed, for
testing things out on Linux.

```
$ vagrant up
...
$ vagrant ssh
...
(httpie-unixsocket) ubuntu@ubuntu-xenial:/vagrant$ http http+unix://%2Fvar%2Frun%2Fdocker.sock/info | jq .RegistryConfig
{
  "InsecureRegistryCIDRs": [
    "127.0.0.0/8"
  ],
  "IndexConfigs": {
    "docker.io": {
      "Name": "docker.io",
      "Mirrors": null,
      "Secure": true,
      "Official": true
    }
  },
  "Mirrors": null
}
```
